<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Duarte, Isabel C.; Afonso, Sónia; Jorge, Helena; Cayolla, Ricardo; Ferreira, Carlos; Castelo-Branco, Miguel (1 May 2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://academic.oup.com/scan/article/12/5/718/3051628">"Tribal love: the neural correlates of passionate engagement in football fans"</a>. <i>Social Cognitive and Affective Neuroscience</i>. <b>12</b> (5): 718–728. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1093%2Fscan%2Fnsx003">10.1093/scan/nsx003</a>. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.worldcat.org/issn/1749-5016">1749-5016</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5460049">5460049</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/28338882">28338882</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Social+Cognitive+and+Affective+Neuroscience&amp;rft.atitle=Tribal+love%3A+the+neural+correlates+of+passionate+engagement+in+football+fans&amp;rft.volume=12&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=718-728&amp;rft.date=2017-05-01&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5460049&amp;rft.issn=1749-5016&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F28338882&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1093%2Fscan%2Fnsx003&amp;rft.aulast=Duarte&amp;rft.aufirst=Isabel+C.&amp;rft.au=Afonso%2C+S%C3%B3nia&amp;rft.au=Jorge%2C+Helena&amp;rf