<li id="cite_note-Cerebellum_and_addiction_review-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Cerebellum_and_addiction_review_17-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Moulton EA, Elman I, Becerra LR, Goldstein RZ, Borsook D (May 2014). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4031616">"The cerebellum and addiction: insights gained from neuroimaging research"</a>. <i>Addict. Biol</i>. <b>19</b> (3): 317–331. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1111%2Fadb.12101">10.1111/adb.12101</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4031616">4031616</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24851284">24851284</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Addict.+Biol.&amp;rft.atitle=The+cerebellum+and+addiction%3A+insights+gained+from+neuroimaging+research&amp;rft.volume=19&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=317-331&amp;rft.date=2014-05&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4031616&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F24851284&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1111%2Fadb.12101&amp;rft.aulast=Moulton&amp;rft.aufirst=EA&amp;rft.au=Elman%2C+I&amp;rft.au=Becerra%2C+LR&amp;rft.au=Goldstein%2C+RZ&amp;rft.au=Borsook%2C+D&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4031616&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReward+system" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></span>
