<li id="cite_note-Cerebellar_systems_and_function_review-18"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Cerebellar_systems_and_function_review_18-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Caligiore D, Pezzulo G, Baldassarre G, Bostan AC, Strick PL, Doya K, Helmich RC, Dirkx M, Houk J, Jörntell H, Lago-Rodriguez A, Galea JM, Miall RC, Popa T, Kishore A, Verschure PF, Zucca R, Herreros I (February 2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5243918">"Consensus Paper: Towards a Systems-Level View of Cerebellar Function: the Interplay Between Cerebellum, Basal Ganglia, and Cortex"</a>. <i>Cerebellum</i>. <b>16</b> (1): 203–229. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1007%2Fs12311-016-0763-3">10.1007/s12311-016-0763-3</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5243918">5243918</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26873754">26873754</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Cerebellum&amp;rft.atitle=Consensus+Paper%3A+Towards+a+Systems-Level+View+of+Cerebellar+Function%3A+the+Interplay+Between+Cerebellum%2C+Basal+Ganglia%2C+and+Cortex&amp;rft.volume=16&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=203-229&amp;rft.date=2017-02&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5243918&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F26873754&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1007%2Fs12311-016-0763-3&amp;rft.aulast=Caligiore&amp;rft.aufirst=D&amp;rft.au=Pezzulo%2C+G&amp;rft.au=Baldassarre%2C+G&amp;rft.au=Bostan%2C+A