<li id="cite_note-Morales2017-20"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Morales2017_20-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Morales, M; Margolis, EB (February 2017). "Ventral tegmental area: cellular heterogeneity, connectivity and behaviour". <i>Nature Reviews. Neuroscience</i>. <b>18</b> (2): 73–85. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1038%2Fnrn.2016.165">10.1038/nrn.2016.165</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/28053327">28053327</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Nature+Reviews.+Neuroscience&amp;rft.atitle=Ventral+tegmental+area%3A+cellular+heterogeneity%2C+connectivity+and+behaviour&amp;rft.volume=18&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=73-85&amp;rft.date=2017-02&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1038%2Fnrn.2016.165&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F28053327&amp;rft.aulast=Morales&amp;rft.aufirst=M&amp;rft.au=Margolis%2C+EB&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReward+system" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></span>
