<li id="cite_note-Wise_2002-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Wise_2002_28-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Wise RA (October 2002). "Brain reward circuitry: insights from unsensed incentives". <i>Neuron</i>. <b>36</b> (2): 229–240. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1016%2FS0896-6273%2802%2900965-0">10.1016/S0896-6273(02)00965-0</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12383779">12383779</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Neuron&amp;rft.atitle=Brain+reward+circuitry%3A+insights+from+unsensed+incentives&amp;rft.volume=36&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=229-240&amp;rft.date=2002-10&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2FS0896-6273%2802%2900965-0&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F12383779&amp;rft.aulast=Wise&amp;rft.aufirst=RA&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReward+system" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></span>
