</li>
<li id="cite_note-34"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Salamone JD, Correa M (8 November 2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4450094">"The mysterious motivational functions of mesolimbic dopamine"</a>. <i>Neuron</i>. <b>76</b> (3): 470–485. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.neuron.2012.10.021">10.1016/j.neuron.2012.10.021</a>. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.worldcat.org/issn/1097-4199">1097-4199</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4450094">4450094</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23141060">23141060</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Neuron&amp;rft.atitle=The+mysterious+motivational+functions+of+mesolimbic+dopamine&amp;rft.volume=76&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=470-485&amp;rft.date=2012-11-08&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4450094&amp;rft.issn=1097-4199&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F23141060&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2Fj.neuron.2012.10.021&amp;rft.aulast=Salamone&amp;rft.aufirst=JD&amp;rft.au=Correa%2C+M&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4450094&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReward+system" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></span>
