<li id="cite_note-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-39">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Soares-Cunha, C; Coimbra, B; David-Pereira, A; Borges, S; Pinto, L; Costa, P; Sousa, N; Rodrigues, AJ (23 June 2016). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4931006">"Activation of D2 dopamine receptor-expressing neurons in the nucleus accumbens increases motivation"</a>. <i>Nature Communications</i>. <b>7</b>: 11829. <a href="/wiki/Bibcode" title="Bibcode">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2016NatCo...711829S">2016NatCo...711829S</a>. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1038%2Fncomms11829">10.1038/ncomms11829</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4931006">4931006</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27337658">27337658</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Nature+Communications&amp;rft.atitle=Activation+of+D2+dopamine+receptor-expressing+neurons+in+the+nucleus+accumbens+increases+motivation&amp;rft.volume=7&amp;rft.pages=11829&amp;rft.date=2016-06-23&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4931006&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F27337658&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1038%2Fncomms11829&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F2016NatCo...711829S&amp;rft.aulast=Soares-Cunha&amp;rft.aufirst=C&amp;rft.au=Coimbra%2C+B&amp;rft.au=David-Pereira%2C+A&amp;rft.au=Borges%2C+S&amp;rft.au=Pinto%2C+L&amp;rft.au=Costa%