<li id="cite_note-Berridge-41"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Berridge_41-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Berridge_41-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Berridge KC, Kringelbach ML (2008). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://lsa.umich.edu/psych/research&amp;labs/berridge/publications/Berridge%20&amp;%20Kringelbach%20Affective%20neuroscience%20of%20pleasure%20Psychopharmacology%202008.pdf">"Affective neuroscience of pleasure: reward in humans and animals"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>Psychopharmacology</i>. <b>199</b> (3): 457–480. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1007%2Fs00213-008-1099-6">10.1007/s00213-008-1099-6</a>. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.worldcat.org/issn/0033-3158">0033-3158</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3004012">3004012</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18311558">18311558</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">20 October</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Psychopharmacology&amp;rft.atitle=Affective+neuroscience+of+pleasure%3A+reward+in+humans+and+animals&amp;rft.volume=199&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=457-480&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3004012&amp;rft.issn