</li>
<li id="cite_note-44"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-44">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Dayan, P; Berridge, KC (June 2014). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4074442">"Model-based and model-free Pavlovian reward learning: revaluation, revision, and revelation"</a>. <i>Cognitive, Affective &amp; Behavioral Neuroscience</i>. <b>14</b> (2): 473–92. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.3758%2Fs13415-014-0277-8">10.3758/s13415-014-0277-8</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4074442">4074442</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24647659">24647659</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Cognitive%2C+Affective+%26+Behavioral+Neuroscience&amp;rft.atitle=Model-based+and+model-free+Pavlovian+reward+learning%3A+revaluation%2C+revision%2C+and+revelation&amp;rft.volume=14&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=473-92&amp;rft.date=2014-06&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4074442&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F24647659&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.3758%2Fs13415-014-0277-8&amp;rft.aulast=Dayan&amp;rft.aufirst=P&amp;rft.au=Berridge%2C+KC&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4074442&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReward+system" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></span>
